This is one of my favorites, but all the OM book apps are great. They're generally more affordable than buying the same books in print too. Plus with these you get professional narration, word reading assistance, and sound effects. And you don't have to wiry about your kids writing on the pages or doing other damage to the book. Compared to other book apps, I prefer the ones made by Oceanhouse Media.  This particular book is full of tongue twisters that are more fun for me to read than other kids books.
